	(gr_text "- 2oz copper\n- U1: TPS54560\n- U4/U5: TC4427\n- U6: XT9080\n- U9: CH224K\n- D1: B650C\n- J1: KF635\n- Q2-Q5: IRLB3813\n- SW1/SW2: 3x4x2 switch\n- L1: 1040 10μH inductor 0530\n- J10-J13: KF301-5.0\n- D4-D7: Optional fly-back diode\n  MBRB2045CT (Schottky)"
