	(gr_text "Max voltage: 24V\nMin voltage: 9V (terminal) / 5v (USB)\nMax total current: 32A -> 18C rise\n25A -> 10C rise\nIO20-IO23 voltage: supply voltage\nMax current per channel: 17A	\n3V3 max current 350mA. \n5V max current 600mA."
